  16,123,"Refi Men wahayini e maa…óa, wonnde: \" Jokku diina Ibraahiima ka naayaaki e diinaaji mehre o jeyanooka e sirkoo…ìe …ìen"
  16,124,"Anndee [mawningol fii] aseweere nden ko wa…óanaa, ko …ìen luutondir…ìe e mayre. Pellet, Joomi maa, ko √±aawoyoowo hakkunde ma…ì…ìe √ëalnde Darngal, e kon ko …ìe luutondiraynoo fii mun"
  16,125,"Noddir e diina Joomi maa kan √±ee√±al e waaju mo∆¥∆¥u. Wennjiraa …ìe e noone …ìur…óo mo∆¥∆¥ude. Pellet, Joomi maa, ko Kanko …ìuri anndude on majju…óo e laawol Makko ngol, ko Kanko kadi …ìuri anndi feewu…ìe …ìen"
  16,126,"Si on yagginay, haray yagginiree yeru no wa…óirano…óon non. Ko si on mu√±√±ike, pellet ko …óum …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥annde mu√±√±ii…ìe …ìen"
  16,127,Mu√±√±o! Mu√±al maa ngal ko sabu Alla tan. Wata a suno fii ma…ì…ìe. Wata wonu …ìittor…óo e kon ko …ìe fewjata
  16,128,"Pellet, Alla no wonndi e …ìen hulu…ìe [Mo] e …ìen mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe"